type: software
title: "SD-A-01-RAG: The Footprint of Retrieval-Augmented Generation Components"
abstract: >-
  A small RAG pipeline study measuring how chunk size, embedding model, and
  retrieval depth trade off cost (latency, memory, energy via CodeCarbon) and
  quality on a sustainability-themed corpus.
